🇮🇳 Bharat Insight – AI Driven Analytics Platform
overview
Bharat Insight is an AI-powered analytics dashboard that visualizes data and allows users to generate insights using AI. The platform is designed with a scalable architecture and modern frontend technologies.



 Live Demo
https://bharatinsightai.netlify.app/

---
 GitHub Repository https://github.com/Niteshkumarasiwal-lgtm/Bharat-insight  

---
 Features

-  Data visualization in table format  
-  Search and filtering functionality  
-  Department-based data simulation (Health & Agriculture)  
-  AI-powered question answering  
-  Fast and responsive UI  

---
 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** Next.js (App Router), React, TypeScript  
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS  
- **Backend:** Next.js API Routes  
- **AI Integration:** Google Generative AI API  
- **Data Source:** Mock API (JSONPlaceholder)  

--

 How It Works

1. The application fetches user data from a mock API.  
2. Data is dynamically rendered in a dashboard table.  
3. Users can filter data using search and department selection.  
4. AI integration allows users to ask questions based on data.  
5. Backend API processes the request and returns AI-generated insights.  

---
 AI Integration

The AI functionality is implemented using a backend API route:

- Sends selected dataset + user query to AI model  
- Processes response  
- Displays generated insights on UI  

--- Challenges Faced

- Handling large dataset simulation efficiently  
- Managing project structure during deployment   

---

 Future Improvements

- Integration with real government APIs  
- Real-time data updates  
- User authentication system  
- Advanced data visualization (charts & graphs)  

---
 Note

Currently, mock APIs are used for development purposes. 
The architecture is designed to easily integrate real-world APIs in future.

